  "detailed_description": "<strong>DON'T LOOK AWAY</strong> is a frightening asymmetrical multiplayer experience!<br>Survive and complete objectives as the Human or terrorize other players as the Entity that can only move when it isn't being watched.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/a0ad832bf50508d06d50e9f405c2f724.webp?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.poster.avif?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.webm?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.mp4?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pure survival horror gameplay that pits you against the most formidable and cunning enemy there is: another player.<br>Complete your objective and survive while your opponent tries to hunt you down.<br>You are alone in the pitch black darkness but the enemy can only move if you look away, your eyes and the flashlight are the only weapons you have.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/b09f44b4a7e452ec48dfbe21981e507a.webp?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/201a3d526afe0653d6ce1c8d538e1739.poster.avif?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/201a3d526afe0653d6ce1c8d538e1739.webm?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/201a3d526afe0653d6ce1c8d538e1739.mp4?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take control of five creepy Mannequins in order to terrorize and eventually kill your opponent.<br>Become invisible, play sounds and create ambushes! Use a variety of abilities and your twisted imagination to toy with your prey.<br>Your only weakness is that you cannot move when your opponent is looking at you.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>DON'T LOOK AWAY</strong> is a frightening asymmetrical multiplayer experience!<br>Survive and complete objectives as the Human or terrorize other players as the Entity that can only move when it isn't being watched.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/a0ad832bf50508d06d50e9f405c2f724.webp?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.poster.avif?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.webm?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/4724352d4cdc777a4acd15288f052b63.mp4?t=1758439311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pure survival horror gameplay that pits you against the most formidable and cunning enemy there is: another player.<br>Complete your objective and survive while your opponent tries to hunt you down.<br>You are alone in the pitch black darkness but the enemy can only move if you look away, your eyes and the flashlight are the only weapons you have.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/b09f44b4a7e452ec48dfbe21981e507a.webp?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557580/extras/201a3d526afe0653d6ce1c8d538e1739.poster.avif?t=1758439311\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_